	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I'm making this palette so I can make sure my artwork can be as graphically consistent as possible.  I started out with some color ramps used in Alisha's Adventure, and arranged them in an NES-like palette.  I can probably expand the number of hues to 16, and have a second level of saturation.<br /><br />Go ahead and edit this palette to fix any think that looks bad.

		
